room_title: Escape room "Dive To Atlantis!" by The Escape Artist in Seattle
room_address: 4517 California Ave SW Suite B, Seattle, WA 98116
room_description:
Things are finally looking up for your Marine Salvage crew, as a wealthy patron has provided you with a submarine and funding to follow his coordinates to the Lost City of Atlantis! You’ve never taken on a task like this, but the payoff is too great to refuse! Your objective is to find Atlantis, bring back the iconic relic, and return to port safely!

You’ve been paid up front, so there’s no real risk…right?
